attachments.text: bug with the cache getter, possibly introduced by python 3.5.  there was a try-catch for TypeError whose purpose was to first check if cached data was json, and if not assume it was plaintext.  it was triggering TypeError before, now it sometimes triggers json.decoder.JSONDecodeError instead of TypeError.
